OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FThis academic year (2025-26) it's
OL,7,Fissued new guidance to schools, which
OL,8,Fsays all 15 and 16-year-olds should
OL,9,Fhave a week's worth of work experience
OL,10,Fplacements. It also recommends that
OL,11,Fall students should have a further
OL,12,Fweek of work-related activities in
OL,13,Ftheir first three years at secondary
OL,14,Fschool.
OL,16,FBut, a new national report shared
OL,17,Fexclusively with ITV News Central
OL,18,Fshows most schools are a long way off
OL,19,Fthat target - and there are huge
OL,20,Fvariations between regions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
