OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FThe Key Group, an organisation which
OL,7,Fsupports schools, has looked at how
OL,8,Fmuch work experience students did last
OL,9,Fyear (2024-25) in Year 10, the year
OL,10,Fwhen most placements take place.
OL,12,FNationally, just 37% of students did a
OL,13,Fweek's work experience, the
OL,14,FGovernment's recommended amount. In
OL,15,Fthe East Midlands, it was just 25%,
OL,16,Fthe lowest of any region. In the West
OL,17,FMidlands, it was 41%. Even in the best-
OL,18,Fperforming region, the South West, the
OL,19,Ffigure was below half at 47%.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
