OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FAcross the country, just 58% of Year
OL,7,F10s did any work experience i.e. at
OL,8,Fleast half a day's worth.
OL,10,FPercentage of year 10 students who did
OL,11,F10+ sessions of work experience in
OL,12,F2024/25, by region
OL,14,FThe report also reveals that pupils
OL,15,Fwith special educational needs, and
OL,16,Fthose who are on free school meals,
OL,17,Fare less likely to do work experience
OL,18,F- and that gap has grown since the
OL,19,Fprevious year.
