OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FChris Kenyon, CEO of the Key Group,
OL,7,Fsays work experience is important for
OL,8,Fputting into context for students why
OL,9,Fthey are at school: "We want to keep
OL,10,Ftrack of how much work experience is
OL,11,Fhappening, both to ensure we know
OL,12,Fwhere the government is going on its
OL,13,Fmission, but critically so individual
OL,14,Fschool leaders and mayors of cities or
OL,15,Fregions can encourage employers to
OL,16,Fstep up."
