OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FBemrose School in Derby offers all its
OL,7,Fstudents a week-long work placement.
OL,8,F16-year-old Dario did his at Barron
OL,9,FMcCann, a city-based company which
OL,10,Fprovides IT support to some of the
OL,11,Fbest-known names in business. For the
OL,12,Fteenager, who has a special interest
OL,13,Fin technology, it was the perfect fit.
OL,15,FDario said, "I feel like it's given me
OL,16,Fa massive insight, and I feel like I
OL,17,Freally do want to go into this area.
OL,18,FIt's just been a fantastic experience,
OL,19,Fand every student in the UK should
OL,20,Fexperience this for themselves."
