OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FScott Watson, Managing Director,
OL,7,FBarron McCann, says they've gone on to
OL,8,Frecruit students who've done
OL,9,Fplacements with them. He says, "There
OL,10,Fare a lot of soft skills that go with
OL,11,Fthe world of work. We all take it for
OL,12,Fgranted, but just coming in at the
OL,13,Fright time in the morning, learning
OL,14,Fhow to interact with colleagues,
OL,15,Flearning how we sign in."
OL,17,FScott explains why work experience
OL,18,Fpupils are so valuable to companies
