OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FClaire Amos, Dario's careers teacher
OL,7,Fat Bemrose School, says, "Any school
OL,8,Fthat hasn't done it in the past,
OL,9,Fyou'll see a change in your young
OL,10,Fperson when they come back, and that's
OL,11,Fwhat it's about. Their aspirations are
OL,12,Fhuge when they come back, and the
OL,13,Fsmile on their faces is why we do it."
OL,15,FFor both schools and businesses,
OL,16,Foffering work experience has its
OL,17,Fchallenges.
