OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FIt's estimated that it costs a school
OL,7,F#20 per pupil per day to place a
OL,8,Fstudent. Multiply that by the number
OL,9,Fof students in a year group, and it
OL,10,Fsoon mounts up.
OL,12,FTeachers also have to spend time out
OL,13,Fof school visiting students on
OL,14,Fplacement and doing safeguarding
OL,15,Fchecks, which puts pressure on
OL,16,Fstaffing resources back in the
OL,17,Fclassroom.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
