OL,3,CEast Midlands schools 'long way off'
OL,4,Cwork experience targets, report finds
OL,6,FChris Kenyon, CEO of the Key Group, is
OL,7,Fquestioning why the East Midlands is
OL,8,Fperforming so poorly compared to the
OL,9,Frest of the country
OL,11,FEmployers have to ensure they have the
OL,12,Fcorrect insurance and health and
OL,13,Fsafety procedures in place when having
OL,14,Fa child on site.
OL,16,FThere are also only a finite number of
OL,17,Fplacements available, and some schools
OL,18,Fsay they find themselves competing
OL,19,Fwith other schools to find openings at
OL,20,Flocal companies.
