OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Work experience
OL,8,Fplays a vital role in ensuring young
OL,9,Fpeople leave school ready for work and
OL,10,Fready for life."Our ambition is for
OL,11,Fevery young person to undertake two
OL,12,Fweeks' worth of work experience and
OL,13,Fthrough the Careers and Enterprise
OL,14,FCompany, we are working to deliver
OL,15,Fthis commitment, with a focus on those
OL,16,Fwho are most disadvantaged or face
OL,17,Fadditional barriers."
